anguage":"en","favoriteCount":0,"replyCount":0,"viewCount":59,"userScreenName":"HiTw93","userName":"Tw93","userIdStr":"1521688129559613440","userFollowers":142177,"userVerified":true,"conversationId":"2049491135522054555","isReply":true,"replyId":"2049636715736842312","mentions":[{"screenName":"SerendiPixels","name":"VBK","userId":"1707951686474735617"}]},{"id":"2049630307901444556","text":"AI can write now. Most AI docs still can’t land. Kami exists to fix that.\n\n👩‍🚒Kami v1.3.0 is out. Good content deserves good paper. Kami is a layout design system for the AI era, built to make AI-generated documents clear, readable, and memorable. It uses one constraint language https://t.co/pKiyFcmUZl","createdAt":"Wed Apr 29 23:22:00 +0000 2026","language":"en","retweetCount":15,"favoriteCount":273,"replyCount":7,"viewCount":17574,"userScreenName":"HiTw93","userName":"Tw93","userIdStr":"1521688129559613440","userFollowers":142177,"userVerified":true,"conversationId":"2049630307901444556","media":[{"type":"photo","url":"https://x.com/HiTw93/status/2049630307901444556/photo/1","thumbUrl":"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HG7Kf3BbkAAGvAc.jpg"}]},{"id":"2049522201049878608","text":"@Faulomi Because I have a $250 max Claude plan, I’m also using Codex 5.5 at the same time.","createdAt":"Wed Apr 29 16:12:25 +0000 2026","language":"en","favoriteCount":1,"replyCount":0,"viewCount":68,"userScreenName":"HiTw93","userName":"Tw93","userIdStr":"1521688129559613440","userFollowers":142177,"userVerified":true,"conversationId":"2049265151736770892","isReply":true,"replyId":"2049518657819345267","mentions":[{"screenName":"Faulomi","name":"Jerome","userId":"142432561"}]},{"id":"2049515877129932840","text":"@Faulomi I mainly use Claude Code CLI for coding, and I use the Claude app more deeply for my day-to-day questions and thinking work.","createdAt":"Wed Apr 29 15:47:17 +0000 2026","language":"en","favoriteCount":0,"replyCount":1,"viewCount":82,"userScreenName":"HiTw93","userName":"Tw93","userIdStr